  "conclusion": "With rowchunk force-flag forwarding fixed, the actual whole-suffix per-row interleaved diagnostic is decisively red and not a fix. Rowchunk2 is no longer the token-green control (L6 token failures on rows1/3), rowchunk3 still has the L6 token failure, both rowchunks gain L5 layer4 QKV/Z drift, and full-attention trace is already over tolerance in layer3 attn_context/residual/mlp_input (attn_context max_abs about 9.03). Whole-suffix per-row interleaving is therefore eliminated as a retained-compatible path and as a hidden-parity repair; the earlier pre-forwarding suffix token movement is superseded.",
